확인된 주요 API (probe 코드 작성 근거):
- AudioContext: constructor(options?) / createOscillator() / createDelay(maxDelayTime?) / createGain()
                 / createBiquadFilter() / destination / sampleRate / state / close()
- OscillatorNode: .type / .frequency (AudioParam) / .start(when?) / .stop(when?)
- DelayNode: .delayTime (AudioParam) / .connect(destination)
- GainNode: .gain (AudioParam) / .connect(destination)
- AudioParam: .value (getter/setter) / setValueAtTime() / linearRampToValueAtTime() 등
- AudioNode: .connect(AudioNode | AudioParam): AudioNode / .disconnect()

